items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!
One cannot live on dank hops alone. Tone down the bitterness and enjoy some smooth flavor. That's 220 different beers with an IBU of 20 or below. Try 5 more for Level 45!

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 455 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 92!

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 200 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 41!

items.checkin_comment: Very very smooth. Almost creamy, it's a very light tasting trip. Honestly probably one of the best IIPA's I've had in a while it's bordering on a perfect score from me. Hides the booze, tastes light and fluffy plus has a beautiful flavour
